# General rules for AI

- Always use kebab-case for file names.
- Typesafety and linting are a must in this project.
- Use our internal definition pattern when defining new features

## Feature organization

- Schema definition: `/src/server/db/schema/[feature].ts` <-- drizzle schema definition
- Queries: `/src/server/domain/[feature]/queries.ts` <-- drizzle queries
- Mutations: `/src/server/domain/[feature]/mutations.ts` <-- drizzle mutations
- Schema validators: `/src/shared/validators/[feature]-schema.ts` <-- shared validators
- tRPC endpoint: `/src/server/api/trpc/routers/[feature].ts` <-- endpoint for internal use
- REST endpoint: `/src/server/api/rest/routers/[feature].ts` <-- public facing apis
- Page: `/src/app/[locale]/[feature]/page.tsx` <-- server side page with prefetch

